Install and run info

====================== Linux =========================
1. Install JOGL libs into maven repo:
go to etc/folder and run mvn-install-libs.sh

2. Compile project (mvn clean install -Dmaven.test.skip)

3. go to space-invaders-gl-game folder and run "mvn scala:run" goal or run runGame.sh in space-invaders-gl folder. 

===================== Windows ========================

1. Install JOGL libs into maven repo:
run etc\mvn_install_common_libs.bat

2. Compile project (mvn clean install -Dmaven.test.skip)

3. Run runGame.bat in space-invaders-gl folder.

NOTES
By default, the game will run in x86 mode. To run it in amd64 please run runGame.amd64.bat
